    {{sectionHeading "Define your Custom Grid"}}
    <p>
        Now that you know how grids work, you can define your own by specifying a few class names and media queries. You can also customize the number of columns that your grid needs.
    </p>
    <p>
        We'll generate a {{code "grid.css"}} file for you based on your requirements that you can download and include in your project.
    </p>


